    "resolution_guidelines": "All assets should be created at 2x resolution for retina displays, then scaled down. Character sprites: 512x512px per frame. UI elements: scalable vectors preferred (SVG) or high-res PNG.",
    "color_palette": "Primary: Yellow (#FFD700), Orange (#FF8C00), Green (#90EE90), Blue (#4A90E2), Pink (#FF69B4). All in pastel variants. No dark colors, no black outlines (use dark gray #333333).",
    "animation_notes": "All animations should be smooth, 60 FPS. Use squash & stretch, easing, bounce effects. Character animations: 8-12 frames per animation. Loop animations for idle, one-shot for actions.",
